create a new folder and set up a virtual environment 
In order to make the assisant work , you need install some libraries 
Follow these commands on command prompt 
1. pip install pipwin
2. pip install pyaudio
3. pip install SpeechRecognition pyttsx3 pywhatkit wikipedia pyjokes 
4. copy the code in assistant.py file into VS code
After all the installations are done -- enter this code in cmd -> python assistant.py
And your assistant is ready
